<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探看着威格尔斯夫人机器人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这么说，真正的威格尔斯夫人逃走了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她是怎么弄出这个洞的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太光滑了，好像是用……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃一惊。“魔术！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探扬起一边的眉毛。“嗯？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼睛发射的x射线看普雷斯托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔术师也是一个机器人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是谁制造了机器人？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转过来去看另外一个犯人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怪人博士！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用眼睛发射的x射线看到怪人博士也是一个机器人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咬了咬嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太可怕了。学校里所有的人都不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>至少有三个犯人逃走了!”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探拿出了手机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来找一下怪人博士总部的地址。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也许去那里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者是去了威格尔斯夫人的空糖果工厂。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。我是‘火箭男孩儿’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转动了一下眼睛。“你好，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔的声音听起来很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想我找到了学校所有的人了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我顺着掉落的铅笔，纸和书走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我被引到了糖果工厂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西说，“威格尔斯夫人肯定跟学校发生的事件也有关联。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我马上去那里，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探收起了手机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，火箭女孩儿，我觉得……火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向糖果工厂飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔等在外面。“这里，罗西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘！”罗西说，“当我是火箭女孩儿的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要用我的真名。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，对。”特勒尔说，“对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到楼上有一扇打开的窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她飞快地飞了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下面，孩子们和老师们都聚在工厂的地板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人站在台子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她手里拿着一根长长的甘草糖绳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西没有看到普雷斯托和怪人博士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赶紧告诉我！谁是火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人对人群说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人跺了跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你们中有一个是火箭女孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是个孩子。也就是说，她在上学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉我，她现在在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不会告诉你任何事情！”潘校长大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”杰克喊道 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西从人群中飞过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就在这儿，威格尔斯夫人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”玛拉喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人恶狠狠地看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞快地飞向坏人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，普雷斯托从角落里出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三，变！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西突然到了工厂的另外一个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门开了。威格尔斯夫人走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脸上带着邪恶的微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个很大的机器人撞开了墙壁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到怪人博士在机器人里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！ 普雷斯托出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。“我被坏人们包围了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>